### Dropdown Schema Builder

{@column flex: 2}
```dart
 ListTile(
  title: Text(schema.label),
  trailing: DropdownButton<String>(
    value: schema.currentValue,
    items: schema.options.map((option) {
      return DropdownMenuItem<String>(
        value: option,
        child: Text(option),
      );
    }).toList(),
    onChanged: (newValue) {},
  ),
);
```

